(hasDescription CaveDepth
  "How deep and dark someone is. Jack is good at gauging this.
   Determines the number of safety stops required for ascent.")

(isa AscentRate MetricNode)
(hasDescription AscentRate
  "Speed at which someone moves from cave to light.
   Too fast → they burst. The patience game.")

(isa SwarmStrength MetricNode)
(hasDescription SwarmStrength
  "Aggregate resilience and capability of the cooperative.
   Strengthens as members return from caves and rejoin.
   Weakens when trust fractures or people are dragged up too fast.")

(isa BeliefThreshold MetricNode)
(hasDescription BeliefThreshold
  "The minimum belief required before someone can believe in themselves.
   Precursor to believing in the work. Precursor to believing in god.
   You, Me, Us — the holy trinity of cooperative belief.")

